WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:21.640 --> 00:00:36.000
 Cut into cubes an onion, a green pepper, a yellow and a red. 

00:01:09.940 --> 00:01:21.460
 Clean a chicken breast by removing the fat and the remains of bones and cartilage. 

00:01:22.400 --> 00:01:28.580
 Even when buying the chicken breast in filet, small bones may appear ... 

00:01:39.500 --> 00:01:55.500
 Cut the chest into medium-sized cubes. 

00:01:59.280 --> 00:02:12.200
 Place the breast cubes in a hot frying pan with a pinch of salt and let it brown. 

00:02:17.680 --> 00:02:28.600
 Add the peppers and the onion and let it brown a little more. 

00:02:31.180 --> 00:02:43.100
 Add one tablespoon of sugar, one of vinegar and two of soy sauce (shoyu). 

00:02:47.340 --> 00:02:57.300
 To thicken the sauce, add a spoonful of diluted corn starch into a cup of water. 

00:03:00.720 --> 00:03:11.140
 Add a handful of shelled peanuts and a good appetite !!! 

